description: Docs/metadata fast-path policy
globs: "{docs/**/*.md,.cursor/rules/**/*.mdc,.cursor/skills/**/SKILL.md,.github/**/*.yml,.github/**/*.md,README.md,.gitignore,.gitattributes}"
